    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Two double-slit experiments are performed using different light sources and different arrangements of slits. In the resulting interference patterns, small-angle approximations are valid.</p><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">In the first experiment, light of wavelength <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lambda sub 1\"><math alttext=\"lambda sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> is incident upon a pair of slits that are a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"d sub 1\"><math alttext=\"d sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>d</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> apart. In the interference pattern formed on a screen some distance from the slits, the distance from the central bright maximum to the adjacent bright maximum is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y sub 1\"><math alttext=\"y sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>. In the second experiment, light of wavelength <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 lambda sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 lambda sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> is incident upon a pair of slits that are a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 d sub 1\"><math alttext=\"2 d sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><msub><mi>d</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> apart. In the interference pattern formed on a screen that is the same distance from the slits as in the first experiment, the distance from the central bright maximum to the adjacent bright maximum is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y sub 2\"><math alttext=\"y sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>. What is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y sub 2\"><math alttext=\"y sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> in terms of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y sub 1\"><math alttext=\"y sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>y</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
